<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Solo"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Frank Ocean"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Blonde"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="426194885"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="QZ5C81600005"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="190055247"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="DEVILISALIE"/></metadata></head><body dur="03:46.409"><div begin="00:00.060" end="03:46.409"><p begin="00:00.060" end="00:02.661" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L0"><span begin="00:00.060" end="00:00.292">Hand</span> <span begin="00:00.292" end="00:00.384">me</span> <span begin="00:00.384" end="00:00.522">a</span> <span begin="00:00.522" end="00:00.768">towel</span> <span begin="00:00.768" end="00:00.988">I'm</span> <span begin="00:00.988" end="00:01.193">dir</span><span begin="00:01.193" end="00:01.401">ty</span> <span begin="00:01.401" end="00:01.611">dan</span><span begin="00:01.611" end="00:01.850">cing</span> <span begin="00:01.850" end="00:02.056">by</span> <span begin="00:02.056" end="00:02.240">my</span><span begin="00:02.240" end="00:02.661">self</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">递给我一条毛巾好吗 自渎后的我肮脏不堪 (dancing by myself = masturbate)</span></p><p begin="00:02.661" end="00:04.497" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:02.661" end="00:02.893">Gone</span> <span begin="00:02.893" end="00:03.094">off</span> <span begin="00:03.094" end="00:03.545">tabs</span> <span begin="00:03.780" end="00:03.930">of</span> <span begin="00:03.930" end="00:04.140">that</span> <span begin="00:04.140" end="00:04.253">a</span><span begin="00:04.253" end="00:04.497">cid</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">撕下那迷幻药的标签吧 (acid=LSD)</span></p><p begin="00:04.497" end="00:06.321" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:04.497" end="00:04.752">Form</span> <span begin="00:04.752" end="00:04.850">me</span> <span begin="00:04.850" end="00:05.003">a</span> <span begin="00:05.003" end="00:05.199">cir</span><span begin="00:05.199" end="00:05.362">cle,</span> <span begin="00:05.362" end="00:05.650">watch</span> <span begin="00:05.650" end="00:05.860">my</span> <span begin="00:05.860" end="00:06.069">jag</span><span begin="00:06.069" end="00:06.321">ger</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">将我围作一圈 看着我如Jagger挥洒 (Mike Jagger The Rolling Stones创始成员之一)</span></p><p begin="00:07.346" end="00:10.315" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:07.346" end="00:07.530">Might</span> <span begin="00:07.530" end="00:07.720">lose</span> <span begin="00:07.720" end="00:07.968">my</span> <span begin="00:07.968" end="00:08.231">ja</span><span begin="00:08.231" end="00:08.507">cket</span> <span begin="00:09.166" end="00:09.353">and</span> <span begin="00:09.353" end="00:09.554">hit</span> <span begin="00:09.554" end="00:09.751">a</span> <span begin="00:09.751" end="00:09.927">so</span><span begin="00:09.927" end="00:10.315">lo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就算卖掉身上的这件夹克 我也要完成这一次独奏 (接前句 Mike Jagger以演出时所穿的昂贵的夹克而闻名)</span></p><p begin="00:10.905" end="00:11.328" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:10.905" end="00:11.033">One</span> <span begin="00:11.033" end="00:11.328">time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只为这一次</span></p><p begin="00:13.811" end="00:16.946" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:13.811" end="00:13.983">We</span> <span begin="00:13.983" end="00:14.231">too</span> <span begin="00:14.231" end="00:14.458">loud</span> <span begin="00:14.458" end="00:14.731">in</span> <span begin="00:14.731" end="00:14.900">pub</span><span begin="00:14.900" end="00:15.096">lic</span> <span begin="00:15.096" end="00:15.305">then</span> <span begin="00:15.305" end="00:15.515">po</span><span begin="00:15.515" end="00:15.746">lice</span> <span begin="00:15.746" end="00:16.001">turned</span> <span begin="00:16.001" end="00:16.326">down</span> <span begin="00:16.326" end="00:16.497">the</span> <span begin="00:16.497" end="00:16.701">func</span><span begin="00:16.701" end="00:16.946">tion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">派对在外喧嚣过分 直到警察来将我们喝止</span></p><p begin="00:16.946" end="00:18.709" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:16.946" end="00:17.053">Now</span> <span begin="00:17.053" end="00:17.153">we</span> <span begin="00:17.153" end="00:17.313">out</span><span begin="00:17.313" end="00:17.551">side</span> <span begin="00:17.551" end="00:17.655">and</span> <span begin="00:17.655" end="00:17.803">the</span> <span begin="00:17.803" end="00:18.002">ti</span><span begin="00:18.002" end="00:18.204">ming's</span> <span begin="00:18.204" end="00:18.470">per</span><span begin="00:18.470" end="00:18.709">fect</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">游荡于街 此刻时分也正好</span></p><p begin="00:18.888" end="00:21.976" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:18.888" end="00:18.973">For</span><span begin="00:18.973" end="00:19.051">got</span> <span begin="00:19.051" end="00:19.208">to</span> <span begin="00:19.208" end="00:19.419">tell</span> <span begin="00:19.419" end="00:19.683">ya,</span> <span begin="00:19.791" end="00:19.919">got</span><span begin="00:19.919" end="00:20.038">ta</span> <span begin="00:20.038" end="00:20.136">tell</span> <span begin="00:20.136" end="00:20.242">you</span> <span begin="00:20.242" end="00:20.401">how</span> <span begin="00:20.401" end="00:20.593">much</span> <span begin="00:20.593" end="00:20.830">I</span> <span begin="00:20.830" end="00:21.049">vibe</span> <span begin="00:21.049" end="00:21.275">with</span> <span begin="00:21.275" end="00:21.976">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">差点忘了告诉你 我与你有多么合拍</span></p><p begin="00:23.370" end="00:25.518" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:23.370" end="00:23.580">And</span> <span begin="00:23.580" end="00:23.820">we</span> <span begin="00:23.820" end="00:24.030">don't</span> <span begin="00:24.030" end="00:24.210">got</span><span begin="00:24.210" end="00:24.441">ta</span> <span begin="00:24.441" end="00:24.855">be</span> <span begin="00:24.855" end="00:25.062">so</span><span begin="00:25.062" end="00:25.518">lo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们都不该独自一人</span></p><p begin="00:27.370" end="00:29.289" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:27.370" end="00:27.540">Now</span> <span begin="00:27.540" end="00:27.781">stay</span> <span begin="00:27.781" end="00:27.973">a</span><span begin="00:27.973" end="00:28.172">way</span> <span begin="00:28.172" end="00:28.470">from</span> <span begin="00:28.470" end="00:28.768">hig</span><span begin="00:28.768" end="00:29.289">hways</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">答应我别再高速公路的狂飙里迷失</span></p><p begin="00:29.289" end="00:30.812" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:29.289" end="00:29.523">My</span> <span begin="00:29.523" end="00:29.748">eyes</span> <span begin="00:29.748" end="00:29.958">like</span> <span begin="00:29.958" end="00:30.176">them</span> <span begin="00:30.176" end="00:30.547">red</span> <span begin="00:30.547" end="00:30.812">lights</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我的眼已泛红光 (红眼是的副作用)</span></p><p begin="00:31.159" end="00:32.700" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:31.159" end="00:31.401">Right</span> <span begin="00:31.401" end="00:31.765">now</span> <span begin="00:31.765" end="00:31.866">I</span> <span begin="00:31.866" end="00:32.051">pre</span><span begin="00:32.051" end="00:32.329">fer</span> <span begin="00:32.329" end="00:32.435">yel</span><span begin="00:32.435" end="00:32.700">low</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在请换上柔和的黄灯吧 (Yellow在交通信号灯中代表放慢速度 也与title Blonde对应 是对Frank双性恋的隐喻)</span></p><p begin="00:32.945" end="00:34.403" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:32.945" end="00:33.231">Red</span><span begin="00:33.231" end="00:33.534">-bone,</span> <span begin="00:33.807" end="00:34.112">so</span> <span begin="00:34.112" end="00:34.225">mel</span><span begin="00:34.225" end="00:34.403">low</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">亲爱的黑人 如此柔和 (是指皮肤带有浅色斑点的黑人 当然这里也有可能在说Redbone乐队)</span></p><p begin="00:34.403" end="00:36.160" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:34.403" end="00:34.632">Fuck</span> <span begin="00:34.632" end="00:34.961">'round,</span> <span begin="00:34.961" end="00:35.109">be</span> <span begin="00:35.109" end="00:35.260">cut</span><span begin="00:35.260" end="00:35.441">ting</span> <span begin="00:35.441" end="00:36.160">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">四处鬼混 我得将你从我的人生剥离</span></p><p begin="00:37.580" end="00:39.952" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:37.580" end="00:37.769">Think</span> <span begin="00:37.769" end="00:38.019">we</span> <span begin="00:38.019" end="00:38.239">were</span> <span begin="00:38.239" end="00:38.453">bet</span><span begin="00:38.453" end="00:38.657">ter</span> <span begin="00:38.657" end="00:39.139">off</span> <span begin="00:39.139" end="00:39.314">so</span><span begin="00:39.314" end="00:39.952">lo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我想我们都孤身一人更好</span></p><p begin="00:42.030" end="00:45.347" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="00:42.030" end="00:42.240">I</span> <span begin="00:42.240" end="00:42.402">got</span> <span begin="00:42.402" end="00:42.649">that</span> <span begin="00:42.649" end="00:43.022">act</span> <span begin="00:43.022" end="00:43.382">right</span> <span begin="00:43.382" end="00:43.459">in</span> <span begin="00:43.459" end="00:43.620">the</span> <span begin="00:43.620" end="00:43.782">Win</span><span begin="00:43.782" end="00:43.980">dy</span> <span begin="00:43.980" end="00:44.194">ci</span><span begin="00:44.194" end="00:44.410">ty</span> <span begin="00:44.410" end="00:44.742">that</span> <span begin="00:44.742" end="00:45.347">night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在大风肆虐的芝加哥夜晚 我们缱绻不眠(Windy City指芝加哥)</span></p><p begin="00:45.347" end="00:46.980" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="00:45.347" end="00:45.553">No</span> <span begin="00:45.553" end="00:45.990">trees</span> <span begin="00:45.990" end="00:46.176">to</span> <span begin="00:46.176" end="00:46.530">blow</span> <span begin="00:46.530" end="00:46.980">through</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">大麻已经抽尽</span></p><p begin="00:46.982" end="00:48.681" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="00:46.982" end="00:47.187">But</span> <span begin="00:47.187" end="00:47.504">blow</span> <span begin="00:47.504" end="00:47.779">me</span> <span begin="00:47.779" end="00:47.886">and</span> <span begin="00:47.886" end="00:48.061">I</span> <span begin="00:48.061" end="00:48.362">owe</span> <span begin="00:48.362" end="00:48.681">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">让我爽上一发吧 这样我便欠你一次</span></p><p begin="00:48.681" end="00:50.400" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="00:48.681" end="00:48.906">Two</span> <span begin="00:48.906" end="00:49.124">grams</span> <span begin="00:49.124" end="00:49.178">when</span> <span begin="00:49.178" end="00:49.366">the</span> <span begin="00:49.366" end="00:49.700">sun</span><span begin="00:49.700" end="00:50.400">rise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">日出时来上两克尽欢</span></p><p begin="00:51.883" end="00:54.257" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="00:51.883" end="00:52.261">Smo</span><span begin="00:52.261" end="00:52.509">king</span> <span begin="00:52.509" end="00:52.915">good,</span> <span begin="00:52.915" end="00:53.119">rol</span><span begin="00:53.119" end="00:53.363">ling</span> <span begin="00:53.363" end="00:53.533">so</span><span begin="00:53.533" end="00:54.257">lo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang