"02:25.223" end="02:25.462">fence</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在孩子的妈妈也不再怨恨着你 她想要的不过是安稳的篱笆护家周全 (picket fence是对于现世安稳生活的一种象征)</span></p><p begin="02:25.462" end="02:28.856" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L40"><span begin="02:25.462" end="02:25.570">And</span> <span begin="02:25.570" end="02:25.859">you</span> <span begin="02:25.859" end="02:26.132">pro</span><span begin="02:26.132" end="02:26.372">test</span> <span begin="02:26.372" end="02:26.464">and</span> <span begin="02:26.464" end="02:26.733">you</span> <span begin="02:26.733" end="02:26.834">pic</span><span begin="02:26.834" end="02:27.006">ket</span> <span begin="02:27.006" end="02:27.291">sign,</span> <span begin="02:27.291" end="02:27.387">but</span> <span begin="02:27.387" end="02:27.611">them</span> <span begin="02:27.611" end="02:27.857">courts</span> <span begin="02:27.857" end="02:28.108">won't</span> <span begin="02:28.108" end="02:28.382">side</span> <span begin="02:28.382" end="02:28.585">with</span> <span begin="02:28.585" end="02:28.856">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你却抗议争夺着 摆脱这抚养权 但法庭上的人不会与你为伍</span></p><p begin="02:29.976" end="02:31.644" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L41"><span begin="02:29.976" end="02:30.225">Won't</span> <span begin="02:30.225" end="02:30.435">let</span> <span begin="02:30.435" end="02:30.664">you</span> <span begin="02:30.664" end="02:31.107">fly</span> <span begin="02:31.107" end="02:31.313">so</span><span begin="02:31.313" end="02:31.644">lo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不会让你一个人潇洒脱身</span></p><p begin="02:35.767" end="02:38.937" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L42"><span begin="02:35.767" end="02:35.985">I</span> <span begin="02:35.985" end="02:36.175">wan</span><span begin="02:36.175" end="02:36.264">ted</span> <span begin="02:36.264" end="02:36.511">that</span> <span begin="02:36.511" end="02:36.787">act</span> <span begin="02:36.787" end="02:37.133">right</span> <span begin="02:37.133" end="02:37.325">in</