吐雾 一个人卷着烟</span></p><p begin="02:50.476" end="02:53.819" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L45"><span begin="02:50.476" end="02:50.695">It's</span> <span begin="02:50.695" end="02:51.173">Hell</span> <span begin="02:51.173" end="02:51.574">on</span> <span begin="02:51.574" end="02:51.989">Earth</span> <span begin="02:51.989" end="02:52.255">and</span> <span begin="02:52.255" end="02:52.475">the</span> <span begin="02:52.475" end="02:52.661">ci</span><span begin="02:52.661" end="02:52.952">ty's</span> <span begin="02:52.952" end="02:53.359">on</span> <span begin="02:53.359" end="02:53.819">fire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这便是地狱降临于人间 城市葬身于火海</span></p><p begin="02:53.819" end="02:56.930" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L46"><span begin="02:53.819" end="02:54.268">In</span><span begin="02:54.268" end="02:54.668">hale,</span> <span begin="02:54.668" end="02:55.119">in</span> <span begin="02:55.119" end="02:55.572">Hell,</span> <span begin="02:55.572" end="02:56.107">that's</span> <span begin="02:56.107" end="02:56.279">hea</span><span begin="02:56.279" end="02:56.930">ven</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">深呼吸吧 即使在炼狱中也有天堂的存在</span></p><p begin="02:57.376" end="03:00.949" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L47"><span begin="02:57.376" end="02:57.528">There's</span> <span begin="02:57.528" end="02:57.773">a</span> <span begin="02:57.773" end="02:58.243">bull</span> <span begin="02:58.243" end="02:58.479">and</span> <span begin="02:58.479" end="02:58.703">a</span> <span begin="02:58.703" end="02:58.911">ma</span><span begin="02:58.911" end="02:59.134">ta</span><span begin="02:59.134" end="02:59.666">dor</span> <span begin="02:59.666" end="02:59.833">due</span><span begin="02:59.833" end="03:00.035">ling</span> <span begin="03:00.035" end="03:00.230">in</span> <span begin="03:00.230" end="03:00.469">the</span> <span begin="03:00.469" end="03:00.949">sky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">天空中 仿佛公牛与斗牛士正在决斗</span></p><p begin="03:00.919" end="03:04.142" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L48"><span begin="03:00.919" end="03:01.339">In</span><span begin="03:01.339" end="03:01.769">hale,</span> <span begin="03:01.769" end="03:02.235">in</span> <span begin="03:02.235" end="03:02.733">Hell,</span> <span begin="03:02.733" end="03:03.197">that's</span> <span begin="03:03.197" end="03:03.400">hea</span><span begin="03:03.400" end="03:04.142">ven</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">深呼吸吧 即使在炼狱中也有天堂的存在</span></p><p begin="03:04.873" end="03:11.167" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L49"><span begin="03:04.873" end="03:06.663">Oh,</span> <span begin="03:06.663" end="03:08.089">oh,</span> <span begin="03:08.089" end="03:11.167">oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">噢</span></p><p begin="03:11.656" end="03:18.289" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L50"><span begin="03:11.656" end="03:13.336">Oh,</span> <span begin="03:13.336" end="03:15.238">oh,</span> <span begin="03:15.238" end="03:18.289">oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">噢</span></p><p begin="03:19.213" end="03:20.602" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L51"><span begin="03:19.213" end="03:20.602">Aye</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">唉</span></p><p begin="03:20.342" end="03:25.061" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L52"><span begin="03:20.342" end="03:20.701">So</span><span begin="03:20.701" end="03:21.493">lo,</span> <span begin="03:23.981" end="03:24.240">so</span><span begin="03:24.240" end="03:25.061">lo</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="03:22.257" end="03:26.694"><span begin="03:22.257" end="03:24.238">(Ah,</span> <span begin="03:24.909" end="03:26.694">ooh)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">啊，呜</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一个人低落 一个人生活</span></p><p begin="03:27.466" end="03:28.620" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L53"><span begin="03:27.466" end="03:27.757">So</span><span begin="03:27.757" end="03:28.620">lo</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="03:27.234" end=